OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy to start, with
OL,6,Fany showers fairly isolated. Some
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells developing for
OL,8,Fthe afternoon, but with a risk of
OL,9,Ffurther isolated showers, these dying
OL,10,Fout later. Warm but breezy, especially
OL,11,Fon coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLargely dry this evening with
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Remaining dry overnight
OL,15,Fwith clear spells, although some
OL,16,Fisolated fog patches may develop. Wind
OL,17,Feasing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
