OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA mostly dry day with plenty
OL,6,Fof sunny spells, although thicker
OL,7,Fcloud and patchy rain are possible for
OL,8,Fa time in the north. Becoming warm or
OL,9,Fvery warm. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FWarm or
OL,12,Fvery warm during this period, perhaps
OL,13,Fhot, with sunny spells. Mostly dry,
OL,14,Fbut risk of heavy thundery showers on
OL,15,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
